{"tid":2202856,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"建制派批鬥 秘書長三經理先後離職  考評局審題主管跳船","createTime":"2020-09-15T02:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T02:35:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9baa2bbc0c6faba0f236958f4fbf9ef1a6334840","tid":2202856,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T02:35:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/2K2OPUIL65GPLFXPZHZAE76XZ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F2K2OPUIL65GPLFXPZHZAE76XZ4%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacdC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=7f240709\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2F2K2OPUIL65GPLFXPZHZAE76XZ4%2F&h=97a7a325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/2K2OPUIL65GPLFXPZHZAE76XZ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n建制派批鬥 秘書長三經理先後離職 <br />\n考評局審題主管跳船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N2lLAqoInJ0sXGf8fAAY4kw9gPQ=/2074x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IJ5LBFEUDJHVBIWOAF4TBLOM6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN2lLAqoInJ0sXGf8fAAY4kw9gPQ%3D%2F2074x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIJ5LBFEUDJHVBIWOAF4TBLOM6E.jpg&h=1f12add8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■考評局近期捲入文憑試歷史科試題風波及受建制報章攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】因文憑試歷史科試題風波而陷入政治風眼的考試及評核局大地震。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：教局罕有索歷史答卷「研究」<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄧力行<br />\n<br />\n據考評局資料，評核發展部主要職責是製備文憑試及教師語文能力評核的試題，並統籌評閱答卷及考生表現評級的工作。現時評核發展主管（前稱總經理）為溫德榮，負責督導各科評核發展，審核文憑試各科試卷等。有曾參與出卷的學者指，若科目的審題委員會成員間有爭議，擔任秘書的科目經理會向評核發展總經理請示。<br />\n<br />\n考評局秘書處共設11個部門，溫德榮為評核發展部主管，早前先後在試題風波後離職的通識科高級經理盧家耀、通識科經理梁紫艷、歷史科經理楊穎宇，均為溫的下屬。溫的直屬上司為去年9月才加入考評局的公開考試總監麥勁生。麥的上司秘書長蘇國生已表明不會續約，明年3月完成三年任期後離任。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉建源憂青黃不接<br />\n<br />\n溫德榮2010年接受傳媒訪問，。。。。。。。。。。，但他視此為終身職業。<br />\n<br />\n溫德榮不時代表考評局出席文憑試記者會。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n教育界立法會議員葉建源認為溫德榮是認真專業工作的考評人員，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mQZMIKrXS3Aty6csnsUTSzNYYQg=/1701x1535/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4FLE45HHRZFKHCEPHU66UYUCYM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmQZMIKrXS3Aty6csnsUTSzNYYQg%3D%2F1701x1535%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4FLE45HHRZFKHCEPHU66UYUCYM.gif&h=3afab2f8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}